From: Rex Lu <rex.lu@mediatek.com>
Date: Tue, 3 Mar 2026 13:27:29 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] mtk: mt76: Add sanity check for wcid->sta being
NULL

fixup! mtk: mt76: rework statistics report for mt7996

add sanity check wcid-> sta is 0 or not due to from fw response wlan_idx may be 0 and happened call trace

Signed-off-by: Rex Lu <rex.lu@mediatek.com>
---
 mt7996/mcu.c | 6 +++---
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+), 3 deletions(-)

diff --git a/mt7996/mcu.c b/mt7996/mcu.c
index 9c99cc2d7..e99905e23 100644
--- a/mt7996/mcu.c
+++ b/mt7996/mcu.c
@@ -7431,7 +7431,7 @@ int mt7996_mcu_get_per_sta_info(struct mt76_dev *dev, u16 tag,
 
 			wlan_idx = le16_to_cpu(rssi->wlan_idx);
 			wcid = __mt76_wcid_ptr(dev, wlan_idx);
-			if (!wcid)
+			if (!wcid || !wcid->sta)
 				continue;
 
 			msta_link = container_of(wcid, struct mt7996_sta_link, wcid);
@@ -7456,7 +7456,7 @@ int mt7996_mcu_get_per_sta_info(struct mt76_dev *dev, u16 tag,
 		for (i = 0; i < sta_num; ++i) {
 			wlan_idx = le16_to_cpu(res->snr[i].wlan_idx);
 			wcid = __mt76_wcid_ptr(dev, wlan_idx);
-			if (!wcid)
+			if (!wcid || !wcid->sta)
 				continue;
 
 			msta_link = container_of(wcid, struct mt7996_sta_link, wcid);
@@ -7468,7 +7468,7 @@ int mt7996_mcu_get_per_sta_info(struct mt76_dev *dev, u16 tag,
 		for (i = 0; i < sta_num; ++i) {
 			wlan_idx = le16_to_cpu(res->msdu_cnt[i].wlan_idx);
 			wcid = __mt76_wcid_ptr(dev, wlan_idx);
-			if (!wcid)
+			if (!wcid || !wcid->sta)
 				continue;
 
